metadata.name: QM NFT #1
metadata.desription: Queen Mermaids is a striking NFT collection of 3000 Mermaids created from hand-drawn elements to celebrating the uniqueness and strength of women around the world.This collection is meant to empower female characters and collectors in the NFT space and beyond.Queen Mermaids was designed to showcase and inspire female creativity. We are focused on creating impact in the NFT space by encouraging women to find their own unique way of expressing themselves creatively.Our goal is to foster an empowered community around a shared love of art, creativity and giving back.
